[/quote]<br>
IMO, it looks nicer[/quote]<br>
It already says Uppercase…</p>
<p><code>public static String optimizeText(String s) {
		for (int i = 0; i &lt; s.length(); i++) {
			if (i == 0) {
				s = String.format( "%s%s",
                         Character.toUpperCase(s.charAt(0)),
                         s.substring(1) );
			}
			if (!Character.isLetterOrDigit(s.charAt(i))) {
				if (i + 1 &lt; s.length()) {
					s = String.format( "%s%s%s",
                             s.subSequence(0, i+1),
                             Character.toUpperCase(s.charAt(i + 1)),
                             s.substring(i+2) );
				}
			}
		}
		return s;
	}</code></p>
          </blockquote>
